9>1 Timothy 4:12<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></H2></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></SPAN></FONT></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P align=left><FONT color=#800080><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 28pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><SPAN style="COLOR: purple"><o:p><FONT face=Arial size=5><FONT color=#000000><FONT size=3>Thank you for your interest in <?xml:namespace prefix = st1 /><st1:place><st1:PlaceName>Peoria</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceName>Christian</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceName>Middle School</st1:PlaceName></st1:place>.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>We are a school of over 250 students in fifth through eighth grades. The middle school campus is located six blocks from the combined elementary and high school campus.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>As a faculty, we strive to serve as Godly role models in every area of our lives.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Whether in the classroom, hallways, or outside of school, it is our goal that the lives of these young men and women are impacted in a positive way by each one of us.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>1 Timothy <st1:time Hour="16" Minute="12">4:12</st1:time> instruct us to set an example in every area of life.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>We are using this verse and theme as our primary focus in the middle<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>school.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>We have a solid and challenging middle school curriculum.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>In addition to our core academic subjects, we also offer band, choir, art, and daily Bible and physical education classes.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Our eight period schedule enables us to offer intramurals and various club activities.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>It would be a privilege to provide you with additional information on <st1:place><st1:PlaceName>Peoria</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceName>Christian</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceName>School</st1:PlaceName></st1:place>.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>You can obtain an information packet or schedule a tour of our facilities by calling our admissions director at (309) 686-4500.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText2 style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT color=#000000><FONT size=3>As you can tell by our middle school home page, we now have additional information available that will help you stay up-to-date with what is going on in the middle school.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Initially, we will have two additional links, Homework Hotline and our Administrative page.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>More pages will be added in the coming weeks.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><o:p><FONT color=#000000 size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT color=#000000 size=3>Should you have specific questions regarding the middle school, please feel free to call me at (309) 681-0500 or e-mail me at </FONT><A href="mailto:eryan@peoriachristian.org"><FONT size=3>eryan@peoriachristian.org</FONT></A><FONT color=#000000 size=3>.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>I also welcome your comments regarding our new website.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Have a great day and thank you for considering </FONT></SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT color=#000000><st1:place><st1:PlaceName><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Peoria</SPAN></st1:PlaceName><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"> </SPAN><st1:PlaceName><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Christian</SPAN></st1:PlaceName><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"> </SPAN><st1:PlaceName><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Middle School</SPAN></st1:PlaceName></st1:place><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">. <o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><o:p><FONT color=#000000 size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT color=#000000>In His Service,<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><o:p><FONT color=#000000 size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT color=#000000>Ed Ryan<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT color=#000000>Middle School Principal<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></FONT><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center>&nbsp;</P></FONT></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT>', 40, 2, 0);
INSERT INTO `main_content` VALUES (296, 1, 0, 0, 'PCS General Info Main Page', 0, '0000-00-00', 1, 0, '0000-00-00', 1, 0, '0000-00-00', 1, '2004-02-12', '2050-06-30', '2004-05-31', '2', '2', '', '2004-02-12', '2004-02-13', 1, 100, '<P>\r\n<P align=center><FONT size=3><STRONG>WELCOME TO PEORIA CHRISTIAN SCHOOL</STRONG></FONT></P>\r\n<P>Now over fifty years old, PCS has a solid reputation of partnering with families to prepare the next generation of leaders and worshipers in our communities.&nbsp; Never has there been a time when the need of a Christian education have been more evident.&nbsp; The coming years will provide unprecedented opportunities for talented, well-educated, spiritually grounded, and confident young people.&nbsp; This fast-paced culture has produced leaders filled with ideas yet lacking in the character and integrity necessary to bring about long-term positive change.&nbsp; Our goal is to assist Christian families and churches, and to foster an atmosphere where consistency of instruction and the modeling of biblical principles is prevalent.</P>\r\n<P>It is our hearts desire to introduce Peoria Christian School to you in a way that Gods blessing and provision shines through.&nbsp; Whether you are simply curious about our school, or you are interested in enrolling your child, please contact us for a tour of our facilities.&nbsp; When you view for yourself the evidence of Gods Hand at work in years past and in the spirit of our school today, you will undoubtedly be blessed.</P>\r\n<P></P>', 41, 2, 0);
INSERT INTO `main_content` VALUES (293, 3, 10, 0, 'Homework Hotline', 0, '0000-00-00', 1, 0, '0000-00-00', 1, 0, '0000-00-00', 1, '2003-10-15', '2004-05-31', '2004-05-31', '99999', '99999', '', '2003-10-23', '2004-02-13', 0, 100, '\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><v:shape id=_x0000_s1026 \r\nstyle="MARGIN-TOP: 24pt; Z-INDEX: 1; MARGIN-LEFT: 455.75pt; WIDTH: 51.4pt; POSITION: absolute; HEIGHT: 124.9pt; mso-wrap-edited: f" \r\ntype="#_x0000_t75" \r\nwrapcoords="19313 52 18551 105 18678 418 20584 889 12579 1412 9911 1621 8386 2510 127 3243 -127 3609 0 4236 508 5073 2414 6747 5464 8420 4447 10094 4193 10931 4320 11924 4701 12604 5464 13441 5591 15115 6099 16788 6353 18462 2414 19299 381 19456 127 19874 889 20136 4701 20972 5718 21548 5845 21548 7115 21548 7496 21548 14612 20972 14485 20606 13976 20136 14104 19299 13722 18462 11308 15952 11689 13441 16391 13441 16645 13127 14231 12604 13214 11768 15882 11768 19440 11297 19313 10931 12833 7584 10927 6747 13849 5910 15501 5073 16264 4236 16391 3400 15501 2563 18169 2144 17788 1726 21600 1360 21600 366 21346 105 20711 52 19313 52"><v:imagedata \r\no:title="AMDOUBT" \r\nsrc="file:///C:\\DOCUME~1\\JORDAN~1.PCS\\LOCALS~1\\Temp\\msohtml1\\08\\clip_image001.wmz"></v:imagedata><w:wrap \r\ntype="tight"></w:wrap></v:shape><FONT size=3><SPAN \r\nstyle="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" align=center><FONT size=3><SPAN \r\nstyle="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"></SPAN></FONT></P><FONT size=3><SPAN \r\nstyle="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"></SPAN></FONT>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" align=center><IMG \r\nalt="Homework Hotline" hspace=0 \r\nsrc="http://www.peoriachristian.org/resources/mbosma/HomeworkHotline.gif" \r\nalign=top border=0></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT size=3><SPAN \r\nstyle="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Homework Hotline is now available on-line!<SPAN \r\nstyle="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Daily assignments will be posted by \r\n</SPAN><st1:time Hour="13" Minute="0"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">1:00 \r\np.m.</SPAN></st1:time><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"> every school day.<SPAN \r\nstyle="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>In addition to the website, homework \r\nwill also be available by calling the </SPAN><st1:State><st1:place><SPAN \r\nstyle="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">California</SPAN></st1:place></st1:State><SPAN \r\nstyle="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"> campus.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; \r\n</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN \r\nstyle="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><o:p><FONT size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN \r\nstyle="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>The on-line Homework Hotline allows us \r\nto provide more information and details than we can do over the phone.<SPAN \r\nstyle="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Not only will we give you the daily \r\nhomework assignments, we will also include the work that was done in the \r\nclassroom, upcoming quizzes and tests, and future \r\nassignments.<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN \r\nstyle="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><o:p><FONT size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN \r\nstyle="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>So whether you were out-of-school or \r\nsimply forgot what your assignments were for today, you can find out by checking \r\nout the Homework Hotline page for your grade.</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN \r\nstyle="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3></FONT></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" align=center><SPAN \r\nstyle="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3><A \r\nhref="http://www.peoriachristian.org/resources/mbosma/HomeworkHotlineGrade5.pdf" \r\ntarget=_blank>Homework Hotline for 5th Grade</A></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" align=center><SPAN \r\nstyle="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3><A \r\nhref="http://www.peoriachristian.org/resources/mbosma/HomeworkHotlineGrade6.pdf" \r\ntarget=_blank>Homework Hotline for 6th Grade</A></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" align=center><SPAN \r\nstyle="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3><A \r\nhref="http://www.peoriachristian.org/resources/mbosma/HomeworkHotlineGrade7.pdf" \r\ntarget=_blank>Homework Hotline for 7th Grade</A></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" align=center><SPAN \r\nstyle="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3><A \r\nhref="http://www.peoriachristian.org/resources/mbosma/HomeworkHotlineGrade8.pdf" \r\ntarget=_blank>Homework Hotline for 8th Grade</A></FONT></SPAN></P>', 1, -3, 37);
INSERT INTO `main_content` VALUES (294, 3, 0, 0, 'Middle School', 0, '0000-00-00', 1, 0, '0000-00-00', 1, 0, '0000-00-00', 1, '2003-10-21', '2005-05-31', '2005-05-31', '99999', '18', '', '0000-00-00', '2004-08-13', 0, 100, '<P align=center><FONT color=#800080><FONT face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><FONT size=6><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 28pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">Peoria Christian&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 28pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">Middle School</SPAN></FONT></FONT></FONT><FONT color=#800080><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 28pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><SPAN style="COLOR: purple"><?xml:namespace prefix = o /><o:p><FONT face=Arial size=5></P>\r\n<P>\r\n<TABLE cellSpacing=1 cellPadding=2 width="100%" border=0>\r\n<TBODY>\r\n<TR>\r\n<TD><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://www.peoriachristian.org/resources/eryan/MSsign.gif" align=baseline border=0></TD>\r\n<TD>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center><SPAN style="COLOR: purple"><EM><FONT size=5><FONT face=Arial><FONT color=#993399>Dont let anyone look down on you because you are young, but <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></FONT></EM></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center><SPAN style="COLOR: purple"><EM><FONT size=5><FONT face=Arial><FONT color=#993399>SET AN EXAMPLE <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></FONT></EM></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center><SPAN style="COLOR: purple"><EM><FONT size=5><FONT face=Arial><FONT color=#993399>for the believers in speech, in life, <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></FONT></EM></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center><SPAN><EM><FONT size=5><FONT face=Arial><FONT color=#993399>in love, in faith, and in purity.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></FONT></EM></SPAN></P>\r\n<H2 style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" align=center><SPAN style="COLOR: purple"><FONT face=Arial><FONT color=#993399>1 Timothy 4:12<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></H2></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText2 style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT color=#000000><FONT size=3>Thank you for your interest in <?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:place><st1:PlaceName>Peoria</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceName>Christian</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceName>Middle School</st1:PlaceName></st1:place>.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>We are a school of over 250 students in fifth through eighth grades. The middle school campus is located six blocks from the combined elementary and high school campus.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>As a faculty, we strive to serve as Godly role models in every area of our lives.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Whether in the classroom, hallways, or outside of school, it is our goal that the lives of these young men and women are impacted in a positive way by each one of us.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>1 Timothy <st1:time Hour="16" Minute="12">4:12</st1:time> instruct us to set an example in every area of life.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>We are using this verse and theme as our primary focus in the middle<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>school.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>We have a solid and challenging middle school curriculum.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>In addition to our core academic subjects, we also offer band, choir, art, and daily Bible and physical education classes.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Our eight period schedule enables us to offer intramurals and various club activities.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>It would be a privilege to provide you with additional information on <st1:place><st1:PlaceName>Peoria</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceName>Christian</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceName>School</st1:PlaceName></st1:place>.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>You can obtain an information packet or schedule a tour of our facilities by calling our admissions director at (309) 686-4500.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText2 style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><o:p><FONT color=#000000 size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText2 style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT color=#000000><FONT size=3>As you can tell by our middle school home page, we now have additional information available that will help you stay up-to-date with what is going on in the middle school.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Initially, we will have two additional links, Homework Hotline and our Administrative page.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>More pages will be added in the coming weeks.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><o:p><FONT color=#000000 size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT color=#000000 size=3>Should you have specific questions regarding the middle school, please feel free to call me at (309) 681-0500 or e-mail me at </FONT><A href="mailto:eryan@peoriachristian.org"><FONT size=3>eryan@peoriachristian.org</FONT></A><FONT color=#000000 size=3>.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>I also welcome your comments regarding our new website.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Have a great day and thank you for considering </FONT></SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT color=#000000><st1:place><st1:PlaceName><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Peoria</SPAN></st1:PlaceName><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"> </SPAN><st1:PlaceName><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Christian</SPAN></st1:PlaceName><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"> </SPAN><st1:PlaceName><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Middle School</SPAN></st1:PlaceName></st1:place><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">. <o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><o:p><FONT color=#000000 size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT color=#000000>In His Service,<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><o:p><FONT color=#000000 size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT color=#000000>Ed Ryan<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT color=#000000>Middle School Principal<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></FONT><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center>&nbsp;</P></FONT></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT>', 39, -1, 0);
INSERT INTO `main_content` VALUES (275, 4, 0, 0, 'Welcome to High School', 0, '0000-00-00', 1, 0, '0000-00-00', 1, 0, '0000-00-00', 1, '2003-12-10', '2005-05-31', '2005-05-31', '5', '18', '', '2003-12-10', '2004-08-13', 0, 100, '<P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 12pt" align=center><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size=4><STRONG>Welcome to the High School of Peoria Christian School</STRONG></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 12pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><FONT size=3>Peoria Christian is well known for quality Christian education. We are pleased that you have become a part of the PC Chargers family or are investigating the possibility.<?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 12pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><FONT size=3>The Administration and Faculty are here to help you, to listen to you, to support you, to inform you, to pray for you, and to remove any barriers that would prevent your student from being all that God wants them to be. We desire to partner with Christian parents to provide an exciting, well-rounded, environment where positive relationships are fostered between students and with the faculty.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>We strive to make this school a place where each student can feel accepted, connected, and valued. We endeavor to use each aspect of school life to teach students to know and experience God for themselves so they will be prepared to meet lifes requirements enjoying the wonder and security in knowing God and making Him known, to the glory of God. Our goal is an environment that stimulates students to achieve their God given potential intellectually, spiritually, physically, and socially.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size=3>We believe Christian parents are looking for a special type of teacher - ones they can trust with their sons and daughters hearts and minds during these years where students are learning to be effective decision-makers and cementing life-long values during these crucial high school years. We have built a faculty team who are life-change teachers. Life-change teachers are ones who love and experience God personally; love and inspire teenage students by using a relational approach to teaching; and love their subject, continually working to stay current and achieve mastery of their subject area.</FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><FONT size=3>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size=3>We trust that the information included in this website will help provide the information you need.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>If not, I invite you to contact me at </FONT><A href="mailto:dwalker@peoriachristian.org"><FONT face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size=3>dwalker@peoriachristian.org</FONT></A><FONT face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size=3> or any of our teachers or support personnel by clicking on the Teachers Directory.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>We would enjoy serving you any way necessary.</FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><FONT size=3>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><FONT size=3>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><FONT size=3>Spreading the Wonder,<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><FONT size=3>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><FONT size=3>Dave Walker<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P></P>', 80, -1, 0);
