\r\n<TD vAlign=top align=right width=20><IMG height=8 src="http://www.wcastl.org/images/bullet2.gif" width=8 vspace=4 border=0></TD>\r\n<TD vAlign=top align=left width=279>\r\n<P><SPAN class=body>Our $378 goal per student is a guideline. Some can\'t afford it and some can give more. Please give in accordance with how God has blessed you.</SPAN></P></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></P>', 64, 2, 0);
