&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; tab-stops: 243.0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">2003-2004<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Dear PCS Students and Parents:<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Welcome!<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>I am excited about what God will do this year in your life and those around you.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>I appreciate your being a part of our PCS Chargers Family.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>We have a big God and we expect big things from Him.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>The administration and faculty are here to partner with you, to pray for you, to motivate you, to help you and to remove any barriers that would prevent you from experiencing a big year.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">The agenda this year has been completely customized.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>We have eliminated pages nobody ever used and added events from our school calendar onto the daily pages for your convenience.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>I want you to use your agenda as a tool to help you accomplish what matters most in your life.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Recording things you need to remember in regards to your academic classes, family plans, church involvement, social and extra-curricular activities all in one central place will help you manage your time so that you can accomplish more.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>So ask God what He wants you to be involved in this year, then schedule it into your agenda.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">The Student Handbook has been revised so you will need to familiarize yourself with the changes now and then refer to it as the need arises throughout the year.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>We ask that you keep and use your agenda throughout the year and that you <U>put in it only things that honor God</U>.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Please realize that if you lose your agenda or if it is defaced in an unacceptable manner, you will be asked to purchase a new one.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">I challenge each of you to follow the advice given in <U>I Corinthians 16:13,14, </U><U>Keep your eyes open for spiritual danger, stand true to the Lord; be courageous; be strong; and whatever you do, do it with kindness and love.</U><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Then ask our Big God to do big things in and through you this year and experience God for yourself.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Enjoy Jesus,<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Dave Walker, Principal<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoHeading7 style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><STRONG><U><FONT size=1><FONT face=Arial>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></U></STRONG></P>\r\n<P class=MsoHeading7 style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><STRONG><U><FONT size=1><FONT face=Arial>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></U></STRONG></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoHeading7 style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><U><FONT size=1><FONT face=Arial>STUDENT PLEDGE  2003-2004<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></U></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 3pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">UNDERSTANDING THE PURPOSE<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">The home and the school are two of the most significant influences in the lives of our young people.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>It is important that students entering and parents preparing to enroll their children in Peoria Christian understand and agree with the purpose and standards of the school.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 3pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Peoria Christian School supports the Christian home and church by preparing students to lead Christ-like lives through a Biblical approach to education.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 3pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<H6><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><U><FONT face=Arial>STANDARDS OF CONDUCT: Guidelines for Christian Living<o:p></o:p></FONT></U></SPAN></H6>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText2 style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face=Arial size=1>Understanding the mission of PCS, we believe the Word of God provides insights for daily living.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Our lives will be enriched by applying these truths in a consistent manner.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>In keeping with these beliefs, it is to be understood that Peoria Christian expects its students to:</FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; tab-stops: list .25in; mso-list: l48 level1 lfo15"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">1.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Actively work at building and nourishing a personal relationship with Jesus Christ.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Studying Gods Word, maintaining an active prayer life, worshipping with fellow believers, making ones self accountable to others, and sharing ones faith are vital components of a growing relationship.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; tab-stops: list .25in; mso-list: l48 level1 lfo15"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">2.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Think about things that are true, noble, right, and pure (Phil. 4:8).</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Avoid influences that distract ones mind, recognizing that what occupies the mind will sooner or later determine ones speech and actions.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; tab-stops: list .25in; mso-list: l48 level1 lfo15"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">3.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Choose your friends and associations carefully (Psalm 1:1).</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>One tends to become like the people with whom one associates.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Understand the progressive nature of sinful activities.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; tab-stops: list .25in; mso-list: l48 level1 lfo15"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">4.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Encourage one another and build each other up (Eph. 4:29-32).<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Avoid destructive, unkind, and unnecessary words or deeds.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Take care that ones attitudes and actions positively influence others, and do not become a stumbling block (Romans 14:13).<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; tab-stops: list .25in; mso-list: l48 level1 lfo15"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">5.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Communicate directly with one another in the spirit of love (Matthew 18:15-17).<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Avoid gossip, talking behind one anothers back or holding bitterness.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; tab-stops: list .25in; mso-list: l48 level1 lfo15"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">6.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Respect authority (I Peter 2:17).<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN>Honor God, obey and respect the laws of our country, the standards of ones parents, and the expectations of ones school.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; tab-stops: list .25in; mso-list: l48 level1 lfo15"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">7.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Be honest and above reproach (Proverbs 8:7).</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Always speak the truth and avoid even the appearance of dishonesty.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Refrain from stealing, lying, cheating, and gambling.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; tab-stops: list .25in; mso-list: l48 level1 lfo15"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">8.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Care for your body as a temple of God (I Cor. 6:19).</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Refrain from the possession and use of alcoholic beverages, tobacco, illegal drugs, abusing prescription drugs or any other harmful substance or activities.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; tab-stops: list .25in; mso-list: l48 level1 lfo15"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">9.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Maintain Biblical standards of morality (I Thes. 4:3-8).</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Save sex for what and when God intended, within the sanctity of marriage.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; tab-stops: list .25in; mso-list: l48 level1 lfo15"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">10.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Demonstrate self-control (James 1:19).</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Be quick to listen, slow to speak, and slow to become angry.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>When you sin, seek forgiveness and make amends.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 3pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<H6><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><U><FONT face=Arial>STUDENT AFFIRMATION<o:p></o:p></FONT></U></SPAN></H6>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">It is my desire to be a part of the student body of Peoria Christian School.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>I affirm that I have read the Student Pledge, and understand its contents, and also affirm that I have read the Student Handbook.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>I will observe the Biblical principles set forth in the standards of conduct, and abide by the expectations in the annual Student Handbook.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>I also have read the Technology Authorized Use Policy and will abide by its requirements.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>I understand that PCS will consciously seek