s, death in the family, doctor or dental appointments, and emergencies.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN><U>Sleeping in or staying home to complete homework assignments, etc. results in an unexcused absence.</U><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face=Arial>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face=Arial>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B><FONT face=Arial>WHEN ABSENT FROM SCHOOL<o:p></o:p></FONT></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face=Arial>On the day students <U>return</U> to school, the student must <U>go to the office, prior to homeroom</U>, to get an admittance pass.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>This pass must be <U>shown to each teacher </U>so the student may <U>receive his/her missed assignments</U>.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN><B>The student will not be admitted to class if this pass is not presented to the teacher.</B></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">A student must be in attendance for at least five (5) full periods to be considered in attendance for a full day.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>To be considered for one-half day of attendance, the student must be in attendance for at least two (2) full periods.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">A student will need to bring in a note on days they must be excused for a dental/doctor appointment.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>This allows us to inform teachers on the days Absentee Sheet and makes it easier for them to check out when they have to leave.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Students in grades 9-12 <U>may sign themselves in and out at the office</U> if arriving or leaving during school hours, but a <U>note from the parent is required stating the reason for arriving late or leaving early</U>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 9pt 0pt 0in"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 9pt 0pt 0in"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 9pt 0pt 0in"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">A student who is <B><U>absent in excess of ten (10) days per SEMESTER</U></B> in a class will likely loose credit for that class.<B><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></B>THE STUDENT WILL BE NOTIFIED UPON RECEIVING HIS<B> <U>FIFTH</U> <U>ABSENCE</U>.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></B>PARENTS <o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 9pt 0pt 0in"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">WILL BE CALLED UPON RECEIVING THE<B> <U>NINTH ABSENCE</U>.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></B>A LETTER WILL BE MAILED HOME IF A STUDENT IS ABSENT FOR A <B><U>TENTH TIME</U> </B>DOCUMENTING THE FACT THAT ANOTHER ABSENCE WOULD MEAN LOSS OF CREDIT FOR THAT CLASS.<B><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN><U>A DOCTORS NOTE IS REQUIRED FOR ANY ABSENCES AFTER THE 10<SUP>TH</SUP> DAY OR CREDIT WILL BE DENIED. <o:p></o:p></U></B></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<H1 style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face=Arial size=2>Absence Notification Form</FONT></H1>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Students are to secure an <B><U>ABSENCE NOTIFICATION FORM</U> </B>from the principal at least a week prior to the extended absence.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>This form must be completed by having each teacher sign in the column provided.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>It must be <U>returned to the office at least three (3) days before the scheduled absence</U>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText3 style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><STRONG><FONT face=Arial>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText3 style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><STRONG><FONT face=Arial>A copy of this form will be sent home to parents via their student if there are significant concerns expressed by the teachers of which the parents need to be made aware.<o:p></o:p></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Students are to complete all class work <U>in advance</U>, if possible, or <U>make prior arrangements</U> with teachers as to the date it must be turned in after they return.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Since the school calendar allows time for vacations, it is suggested that whenever possible, parents should arrange their vacations to coincide with school vacation time.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Each absence will be considered on an individual basis, taking into account the purpose or reason of the absence, as well as the students past academic and attendance records.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<H1 style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face=Arial size=2>Missing Classes to do Homework</FONT></H1>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face=Arial>All students are expected to complete research papers and homework outside class time.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Allowing students to stay home during regular class times to get research papers and homework completed introduces several problems.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>This practice:</FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face=Arial>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; tab-stops: list .25in; mso-list: l36 level1 lfo43"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">1.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Does not encourage proper planning and commitment.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; tab-stops: list .25in; mso-list: l36 level1 lfo43"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">2.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Creates an unfair advantage over students who do assignments as expected.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; tab-stops: list .25in; mso-list: l36 level1 lfo43"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">3.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Hinders unity and respect between themselves and other students and faculty.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; tab-stops: list .25in; mso-list: l36 level1 lfo43"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">4.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">It is not an excused absence.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Please do not allow your student to cut classes to avoid taking a test or to work on research papers or other homework.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Game Day Attendance<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B><U><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">TO PARTICIPATE IN GAMES, ATHLETES MUST ARRIVE AT SCHOOL BY THE 5<SUP>TH</SUP> PERIOD</SPAN></U></B><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">.</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>If a student is too sick to be in school, he/she should not be playing in the game.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">PE Absence</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">If a student cannot participate in music or physical education, a note of explanation from the parents must be presented to the teacher.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>For extended periods of non-participation, <U>a note from the attending physician should be provided</U>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">TRUANCY</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Absence without the parents and/or schools knowledge and permission is considered truancy.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>This includes not coming to school or skipping a class.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>The <U>first truancy will result in an in-school suspension</U> and a parent conference.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Subsequent truancies will result in harsher discipline and academic penalties.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">TARDIES</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Punctuality is a virtue that should be cultivated in everyones life.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>We expect our students to be here before school begins each day.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><SPAN style="FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">TARDIES TO SCHOOL</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"> - All students <U>who are tardy in the morning are to go directly to Homeroom</U>.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Students who arrive after Homeroom must stop at the office for a tardy slip.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Each student is allowed four (4) tardies for any reason during a marking period.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN><B>A FIFTH TARDY TO SCHOOL WILL MEAN AN ADMINISTRATIVE DETENTION WILL BE GIVEN.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>AN ADMINISTRATIVE DETENTION WILL BE GIVEN FOR EACH LATE ARRIVAL TO SCHOOL AFTER THE FOURTH TARDY DURING A 9-WEEKS PERIOD (i.e. for the 5<SUP>th</SUP> tardy a detention will be given, for the 6<SUP>th</SUP> tardy a detention will be given, for the 7<SUP>th</SUP> tardy a detention will be given, etc.).</B><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><SPAN style="FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">TARDIES TO CLASSES</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"> - The first tardy during a nine-week period will result in a warning.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>A second tardy will mean an Administrative Detention.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Every tardy thereafter will mean an additional Administrative Detention.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><SPAN style="FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">If a teacher detains a student, he/she may write the student a note in the<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>hall pass section of the students agenda.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>This will not be counted as a tardy.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">NOTE:<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Tardies may be waived by the administration for inclement weather, doctor and dental appointments, etc.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">INCLEMENT WEATHER</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-