-medium-gap; mso-border-left-alt: thin-thick-medium-gap; mso-border-bottom-alt: thick-thin-medium-gap; mso-border-right-alt: thick-thin-medium-gap; mso-border-color-alt: windowtext; mso-border-width-alt: 6.0pt" align=center><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'">ATHLETICS</SPAN></B></P></DIV></DIV></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'"><FONT size=3><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN><o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT size=3><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<H1 style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT size=2><FONT face=Arial>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></H1>\r\n<H1 style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face=Arial size=2>Athletic Fees</FONT></H1>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face=Arial>A student must sell ten boxes of fruit or pay a $75.00 participation fee to be involved in one sport or $100.00 participation fee to be involved in two or more sports each year.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>This fee is due prior to the beginning of the season in which a student participates.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>This is an annual requirement not for each season.</FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">All athletes are required to have an annual physical exam.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>A Saturday is set up for physicals to be given at school during summer months for a nominal fee.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">All athletes must meet the academic eligibility outlined in the Athletic Handbook.</SPAN><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3> </FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'">Athletes, cheerleaders and drill team must have all forms signed prior to practice.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'">Athletic Ineligibility<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Athletics play a vital part in the lives of our students.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>As part of a team, our students learn responsibility, respect, skills, companionship, and sportsmanship, among other important life skills.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>It is our desire that every student have the opportunity and privilege to participate.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Participation in Peoria Christian athletics is a privilege and must be treated as such.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>When academics and behavior become unacceptable, privileges, such as participation in athletics, may be placed in jeopardy.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>In addition to fulfilling the requirements as outlined in the Athletic Handbook, all students must fulfill the following academic and behavioral standards in order to remain eligible to participate:<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; tab-stops: list .5in; mso-list: l33 level1 lfo33"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><SPAN style="FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><U><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Academic Ineligibility</SPAN></U><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">:<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Every Friday during the sports season, grades will be solicited from the teachers of each athlete.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Eligibility will be determined based on a point system for the grades of D and F.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>A grade of D will be the equivalent of 1 point and an F will be the equivalent of 2 points.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Students receiving a total of 4 points (e.g., two Fs; one F and two Ds; etc.) will be ineligible until grades are reviewed the following week and it is determined that the student falls below the 4 point level.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Typically, ineligibility will run from Tuesday through the following Monday.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<H1 style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center><FONT face=Arial size=2>Tri-County Conference Schools</FONT></H1>\r\n<P>\r\n<TABLE style="BORDER-RIGHT: medium none; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; BORDER-BOTTOM: medium none; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; mso-table-layout-alt: fixed; mso-padding-alt: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt" cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 border=1>\r\n<TBODY>\r\n<TR>\r\n<TD style="BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 0.5pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 0.5pt solid; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0in; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 0.5pt solid; WIDTH: 99.6pt; PADDING-TOP: 0in; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 0.5pt solid; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent" vAlign=top width=133>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">Eureka<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P></TD>\r\n<TD style="BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 0.5pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 0.5pt solid; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0in; BORDER-LEFT: #d4d0c8; WIDTH: 99.6pt; PADDING-TOP: 0in; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 0.5pt solid; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt" vAlign=top width=133>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi