ay<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face=Arial><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">Special </SPAN><st1:place><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">Holiday</SPAN></st1:place><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"> Celebrations<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT face=Arial>Colonial Day<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face=Arial><st1:place><st1:PlaceName><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">Old-Fashion</SPAN></st1:PlaceName><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"> </SPAN><st1:PlaceType><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">School</SPAN></st1:PlaceType></st1:place><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"> Day<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT face=Arial>Principals Picnic<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>', 76, -1, 0);
INSERT INTO `main_content` VALUES (266, 1, 10, 0, 'Statement of Faith', 0, '0000-00-00', 1, 0, '0000-00-00', 1, 0, '0000-00-00', 1, '2003-12-02', '2014-05-31', '2004-05-31', '10', '10', '', '2003-12-02', '2004-01-20', 0, 100, '<SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=5>\r\n<P class=MsoSubtitle style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" align=center><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><STRONG>Statement of Faith<?xml:namespace prefix = o /><o:p></o:p></STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><STRONG>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><I><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>The authority for the Constitution of this Association is the Holy Scripture and its teaching as understood in the literal, grammatical, and cultural sense and shall be binding on this Association as long as it exists.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Every statement, regulation, and provision of the constitution and by-laws of this Association must be in harmony with the relevant teaching of the Scriptures.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>No statement, policy, or action shall be taken that infringes upon or contradicts the teaching of the Scriptures as interpreted by the following doctrinal statement:<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></I></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; tab-stops: 65.0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 60pt; TEXT-INDENT: -60pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>Section 1:<SPAN style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>We believe the Scriptures of the Old and New Testaments are inspired by God, and are inerrant in the original writings, and that they are of supreme and final authority in faith and life.<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 60pt; TEXT-INDENT: -60pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 60pt; TEXT-INDENT: -60pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>Section 2:<SPAN style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>We believe in one God, eternally existent in three persons:<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Father, Son, and Holy Spirit.<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 60pt; TEXT-INDENT: -60pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 60pt; TEXT-INDENT: -60pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>Section 3:<SPAN style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>We believe in the deity of our Lord Jesus Christ, in His virgin birth and His sinless life, in His miracles, in His vicarious and atoning death through His shed blood, in His bodily resurrection, in His ascension to the right hand of the Father, and in His future personal return in power and glory.<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 60pt; TEXT-INDENT: -60pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 60pt; TEXT-INDENT: -60pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>Section 4:<SPAN style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>We believe that for the salvation of the lost and sinful man, regeneration by the Holy Spirit is absolutely essential.<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 60pt; TEXT-INDENT: -60pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>Section 5:<SPAN style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>We believe in the resurrection of both the saved and the lost; they that are saved unto the resurrection of life, and they that are lost unto the resurrection of damnation.<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 60pt; TEXT-INDENT: -60pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>Section 6:<SPAN style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>We believe in the spiritual unity of all believers in our Lord Jesus Christ. <o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoSubtitle style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"></FONT></SPAN></P>', 77, 2, 0);
INSERT INTO `main_content` VALUES (289, 10, 30, 0, 'Golf Classic', 0, '0000-00-00', 1, 0, '0000-00-00', 1, 0, '0000-00-00', 1, '2003-12-04', '2004-05-31', '2004-05-31', '6', '6', '', '2003-12-04', '2004-02-13', 1, 100, '<P></P><B><I>\r\n<P align=center><IMG style="WIDTH: 211px; HEIGHT: 177px" height=1333 alt="" hspace=2 src="http://www.peoriachristian.org/uploads/jkammerer_2_Team on the green_1070570577_100_0794.JPG" width=1074 align=left vspace=2 border=5><IMG style="WIDTH: 227px; HEIGHT: 176px" height=1291 alt="" hspace=2 src="http://www.peoriachristian.org/uploads/jkammerer_0_Broken Club_1070570577_100_0791.JPG" width=798 align=right vspace=2 border=5><IMG style="WIDTH: 188px; HEIGHT: 174px" height=1391 alt="" hspace=2 src="http://www.peoriachristian.org/uploads/jkammerer_1_PCS Golf Team_1070570577_100_0773.JPG" width=1100 align=bottom vspace=2 border=5></P>\r\n<P align=center>Thank you for making 7th Annual Fall Classic a Success.</P>\r\n<P align=center></P></B></I>\r\n<P>We would like to thank all the sponsors who helped out and financially supported the Fall Classic. The weather held out for one more day and we thanked God for that! Everyone had a wonderful time and the only casualties from the outing were one window, one club&nbsp;and a post along the cart path. I have to thank all the volunteers who woke up early Saturday morning and were willing to help set up and man holes for the contests. Weaver Ridge provided a wonderful lunch and the course was breath taking. I want to thank Patrick Hauer for being our chair person for this event, he did a great job.&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>Our 8th Annual Golf Classic will be June 22nd, 2004 at Pine Lakes Golf Course. Registration begins at 12:00 pm and&nbsp;shotgun start at 1:00 pm.&nbsp;&nbsp;Cost for outing&nbsp;is $100&nbsp;per preson. &nbsp;Steak dinner and awards banquet to follow outing. If you any ideas or wish to participate in the planning of&nbsp;this years event please contact the Advancement Office. You can call 309-686-4500 Ext: 33 or email jkammerer@peoriachristian.org.</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>', 35, 2, 0);
INSERT INTO `main_content` VALUES (290, 10, 40, 0, 'Material Needs', 0, '0000-00-00', 1, 0, '0000-00-00', 1, 0, '0000-00-00', 1, '2003-12-04', '2004-08-30', '2004-08-30', '6', '6', '', '2003-12-04', '2004-08-03', 0, 100, '<P>\r\n<P>Peoria Christian School is thankful for the generous gifts that have been given over the years.&nbsp; Many of the&nbsp;items listed&nbsp;below are essential for the daily productive operation of the school. Please review the list and if you feel compelled to contribute contact the Advancement Department at 309-686-4500 Ext: 33 or email <A href="mailto:jkammerer@peoriachristian.org">jkammerer@peoriachristian.org</A>. </P>\r\n<P align=center><STRONG><U>Office and Schools</U></STRONG></P>\r\n<P align=center>Color Laser Printer</P>\r\n<P align=center>Copy Machine</P>\r\n<P align=center>15 Passenger Bus</P>\r\n<P align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P align=center><STRONG><U>Maintenance &amp; Grounds</U></STRONG>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P align=center>Hammer Drill-portable cordless</P>\r\n<P align=center>1/2 Drill 9 amp</P>\r\n<P align=center>Power Miter Box</P>\r\n<P align=center>Snow Thrower</P>\r\n<P align=center>&nbsp;</P>', 36, -1, 0);
INSERT INTO `main_content` VALUES (291, 10, 20, 0, 'Ways to support PCS', 0, '0000-00-00', 1, 0, '0000-00-00', 1, 0, '0000-00-00', 1, '2003-11-19', '2004-05-31', '2004-05-31', '6', '6', '', '2003-11-19', '2004-02-13', 0, 100, '<P align=center><STRONG>Here are ways that you can support/participate at Peoria Christian School</STRONG></P>\r\n<P align=center>\r\n<TABLE cellSpacing=1 cellPadding=2 width="100%" border=1>\r\n<TBODY>\r\n<TR>\r\n<TD>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P align=center><STRONG>Prayer</STRONG></P>\r\n<P>Your Prayer support is most important. Here are some areas that you could pray for the school.</P>\r\n<P>1. The PCS Board</P>\r\n<P>2. Administration<BR>3. Staff</P>\r\n<P>4. Students</P>\r\n<P>5. Advancement </P>\r\n<P>6. Our deficit</P>\r\n<P>7. The ministry of PCS</P>\r\n<P>8. 7th Annual Auction Success</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P></TD>\r\n<TD>\r\n<P align=center><STRONG></STRONG>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P align=center><STRONG>Volunteer</STRONG></P>\r\n<P>PCS could not minister without God\'s blessing and the&nbsp;involvement of parents PCS. There are many areas that you can chose to serve in.</P>\r\n<P>The Annual Banquet offers opportunity to serve in:</P>\r\n<UL>\r\n<LI>Cochair of banquet committee \r\n<LI>Decorations \r\n<LI>Advertising/promotions \r\n<LI>Set up &amp; tear down \r\n<LI>Audio \r\n<LI>Sponsor solicitation \r\n<LI>Registration ticket sales</LI></UL>\r\n<P>The Golf Classic offers opportunity to serve in:</P>\r\n<UL>\r\n<LI>Cochair of golf committee \r\n<LI>Sponsor solicitation \r\n<LI>Advertising/promotions \r\n<LI>Prizes \r\n<LI>Event day pictures</LI></UL>\r\n<P>The Auction offers opportunity to serve in:</P>\r\n<UL>\r\n<LI>Cochair of Baskets \r\n<LI>Cochair of Volunteers \r\n<LI>Cochair of Aquisitions \r\n<LI>Publicity \r\n<LI>Catering</LI></UL>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P></TD>\r\n<TD>\r\n<P align=center><STRONG>Programs</STRONG></P>\r\n<P align=center><STRONG>K-Mart School Spirit Program</STRONG></P>\r\n<P>Go to your local K-Mart and sign up at customer service and receive your <B>School Spirit Card. </B>Choose PCS as the recipient. Before each purchase present that card to the checker and a portion of your purchase will be donated back to PCS. </P>\r\n<P></P>\r\n<P>Dont forget you can purchase K-Mart <I>Scrip</I> at the PCS business office.</P><B>\r\n<P>Targets-</B>Take Charge of Education which donates <I>1%</I> of Target Visa and Target Guest Card purchases made at Target and www.target.com, and <I>%</I> of Target Visa purchases made elsewhere, to Peoria Christian School. Call the 800 number on the back of your Target Visa or Guest Card and specify that you want PCS to receive the Education Funds. Thats all it takes to start helping the school.</P>\r\n<P><BR>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><STRONG>Gordon Food Services Fun Funds.</STRONG><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>You can help raise money for PCS simply by filling out the prepaid Business Reply Card that is at&nbsp;GFS and drop it in the mail. You will receive a Fun Funds card which identifies you as a <?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:place><st1:PlaceName>Peoria</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceName>Christian</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceName>School</st1:PlaceName></st1:place> supporter.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Present this card before every purchase at the GFS Marketplace and GFS will return a percentage of purchases back to the school.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>The more you shop at GFS the more you bless the school.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></P>', 37, 2, 0);
